comments.body:
I had that originally but had some problems, don't remember what. Will try again on next push.
Edit: it's used in `std::overflow_error` which expects a `String`:
```C++
  _LIBCPP_HIDE_FROM_ABI explicit overflow_error(const string& __s) : runtime_error(__s) {}
  _LIBCPP_HIDE_FROM_ABI explicit overflow_error(const char* __s) : runtime_error(__s) {}
```

